All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
The main class of the CityLibrary application.
Book
The Book class represents a book in the library, with a title, author, available quantity, and total quantity.
Catalog
The Catalog class represents a collection of books in the library.
ConsoleView
A class that implements the View interface and provides a console-based user interface for the City Library application.
FilePersistency
This class provides file-based implementation of the Persistency interface.
LibraryController
The LibraryController class is responsible for managing the library's catalog and readers.
Persistency
This interface defines the methods for saving and loading data from a file.
Reader
Represents a reader who can borrow books from the library.
View
The View interface defines the methods that a view implementation should provide.
